[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0909","title":"Microsoft Windows 多宿主系统 IP 源路由绕过漏洞","description":"Windows 98 SE、Windows NT、Windows 95 及 Terminal Server 等多宿主 Windows 系统存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的包含 IP 选项的畸形数据包，绕过 IP 源路由限制，从而实施网络劫持或中间人攻击。该漏洞影响多款早期 Windows 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0909"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.537","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-038 提供的补丁程序，该补丁修复了 IP 源路由绕过漏洞，并新增通过注册表 DisableIPSourceRouting (HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters) 设为 2 以完全禁用源路由的功能。由于 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 均已停止支持且不再接收更新，建议尽快升级到受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+），同时在网络边界防火墙和路由器上配置策略丢弃带有 IP 源路由选项（Loose Source Route 和 Strict Source Route）的入站数据包作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238453","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/646","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0521","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0521.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0787","title":"SSH Communications Security SSH 1.2.27 身份验证套接字符号链接跟随漏洞","description":"SSH 1.2.27 认证代理中存在符号链接竞争（symlink race）漏洞。当 SSH 服务端以 root 权限运行并启用认证代理转发（authentication agent forwarding）时，会在 /tmp/ssh-{用户名}/ 目录下创建 UNIX 域套接字，套接字文件名基于当前进程 PID 生成且可预测。服务端在创建该套接字时未验证路径是否存在符号链接，直接跟随符号链接写入文件。攻击者可在 sshd 创建套接字之前，提前在该目录下建立指向敏感文件（如 /etc/nologin）的符号链接，导致服务端以 root 权限在符号链接指向的位置创建套接字文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件或拒绝合法用户登录。该漏洞影响 SSH Communications Security SSH 1.2.27，CVSS v2 评分 2.1，危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0787"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.440","remediation":"立即升级 SSH Communications Security SSH 至 1.2.27 之后的安全修复版本，或迁移至 OpenSSH 替代。临时缓解措施：在 sshd_config 中禁用 AuthenticationAgentForwarding 选项，重启 SSH 服务；同时清理 /tmp/ssh-* 目录下的所有预创建符号链接，确保该目录仅由真实用户所有且权限为 0700，防止攻击者提前创建恶意链接覆盖 /etc/nologin 等关键系统文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93760201002154&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93832856804415&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/660","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19510","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7af4f92412aedbb5d40436f8e5560c660110d48c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0787","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0787.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5164f1de7b3f58f6409a5df271b515e5969e7d38/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-93v8-gx5g-v586/GHSA-93v8-gx5g-v586.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--76e0f930-9120-4d0c-b52e-6cf26ac3a600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/c77faccf7cf2fb75741042a2f81e7d733860667d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0521.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1168","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0886","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RASMAN 权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的远程访问服务管理器（RASMAN）存在安全描述符配置缺陷，允许本地用户通过服务控制管理器将 RASMAN 指向备用位置，从而以 SYSTEM 权限执行任意代码。攻击者需具有本地登录权限，利用该配置漏洞可完全控制受影响的 Windows NT 4.0 系统（包括 SP1~SP6 版本），实现权限提升。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0886"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.700","remediation":"最彻底的解决方案是升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且不再发布安全更新。如无法升级，可禁用 Remote Access Service（RAS）服务，并修改注册表中 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\RASMAN 项的权限，仅允许 Administrators 组访问，同时通过组策略限制非授权用户对服务控制管理器的操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ242294","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/645","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19502"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0333","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0333.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0704","title":"Berkeley am-utils amd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Berkeley 自动挂载守护进程（amd）的日志记录功能存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行或服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS 3.1/4.0.1、FreeBSD 3.0/3.1/3.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等系统，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0704"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.043","remediation":"升级 am-utils 至 6.0 以上版本，或应用厂商安全补丁：FreeBSD 用户升级至 3.3 及以上版本，RedHat 用户安装 RHSA-1999:032 提供的 am-utils 更新包。如无法升级，在 inetd 配置中禁用 amd 服务或限制 amd 仅监听可信网络接口。对于 BSD/OS 用户，联系厂商获取 4.1 版本的修复补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/614","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19479","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fec368cf82886628cf7251fa55925507d7e50c60/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0704.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0704","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0704.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0704.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1906.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1905.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_amd.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a1a39f51-3877-479a-ad5b-fc201e242044.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0333.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0890","title":"iHTML Merchant 代码执行信息泄露漏洞","description":"iHTML Merchant 存在代码解析安全漏洞。攻击者可通过向该系统发送特制请求利用代码解析错误，导致服务器执行任意命令或泄露敏感信息（如数据库凭据、配置数据）。该漏洞可在未经认证的情况下远程触发，攻击复杂度低，且无需用户交互。此漏洞影响 iHTML Merchant 多版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0890"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.180","remediation":"建议立即停用并重新安装 iHTML Merchant 6.0 或更高版本，通过官方网站下载并应用完整的补丁包。进行安全代码审计，确保所有用户输入都经过 proper 验证和转义，并在服务器上应用最新的安全补丁包以修复代码解析漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ihtmlmerchant.com/support_patches_feedback.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/694"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0682.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0707","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0707.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0907","title":"sccw 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"sccw (soundcard control wrapper) 程序存在任意文件读取漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序对文件权限检查的缺陷，可读取系统中的任意文件，包括 /etc/passwd 等敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版，攻击需拥有本地用户账号，条件受限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0907"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.287","remediation":"立即移除 sccw 的 setuid 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/sccw`，防止本地用户利用其特权读取任意系统文件。如非必要，建议直接卸载该软件包：`apt-get remove sccw` 或 `yum remove sccw`。若必须使用，限制可执行权限仅授予受信任用户：`chmod 750 /usr/bin/sccw && chown root:audio /usr/bin/sccw`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0907"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0707.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0953","title":"WWWBoard 2.0 远程密码泄露漏洞","description":"WWWBoard 2.0 存在安全配置缺陷，系统将加密后的用户密码以明文文件 passwd.txt 形式存储在 Web 根目录下，导致远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问该文件路径获取所有用户的密码哈希值。该漏洞影响 WWWBoard 2.0 版本，危害等级严重。攻击者获取密码哈希后可进行离线破解，进一步威胁系统安全。建议升级版本或限制敏感文件访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0953"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.863","remediation":"立即将 passwd.txt 移出 Web 可访问目录（如移至 www 根目录之外），并通过 .htaccess 或 Web 服务器配置禁止访问 *.txt 文件。建议停止使用已停止维护的 WWWBoard 2.0，迁移至支持安全密码存储的现代论坛系统，并对所有受影响用户强制重置密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0953","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/3065"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0744","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0744.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0954","title":"WWWBoard 默认用户名密码弱配置漏洞","description":"WWWBoard 是一款基于 Perl 的 Web 论坛系统，其默认安装中硬编码了默认管理员用户名和密码（如 admin/admin）。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接使用默认凭据登录管理后台，获取完全控制权限，进而可删除、修改或窃取论坛数据。该漏洞影响所有使用默认配置的 WWWBoard 版本，利用方式简单，只需使用已知的默认凭据登录管理界面即可。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0954"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即修改 WWWBoard 配置文件中硬编码的默认管理员用户名和密码（默认常见组合为 admin/admin 等），禁止使用出厂默认凭据。由于 WWWBoard 已多年无人维护且不再更新，建议将论坛数据迁移至仍受支持的开源论坛系统（如 Discourse、Flarum、phpBB），并在过渡期间通过 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置 IP 白名单限制管理后台访问路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/649","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0954"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0744.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0817","title":"Lynx 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Lynx WWW 客户端在处理 telnet 等协议时，会调用外部程序处理请求，但未对传入的命令行参数进行有效过滤，导致远程攻击者可通过构造特制的 URL 链接，向 Lynx 传递恶意命令行参数，从而在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 Lynx 版本，危害等级严重，攻击者可通过诱使用户点击恶意链接完成利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0817"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.183","remediation":"升级到 Lynx 2.8.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了传递不可信参数给外部程序（如 telnet）的问题。如无法升级，可在 Lynx 配置中将 `TRUSTED_LYNXCGI` 和 `ALLOW_USER_OPTIONS` 设为关闭，并禁用对外部协议处理程序的自动调用作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0817"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0249","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0689","title":"Sun CDE dtspcd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE（Common Desktop Environment）中的 dtspcd 守护进程存在符号链接攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 dtspcd 进程以高权限执行任意命令，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 及 CDE 2.1.20 等版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，危害等级高。厂商已发布相关安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0689"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.173","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 提供的补丁程序（Solaris 7 SPARC 补丁 107018-xx，x86 补丁 107019-xx），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 \"dtspc\" 行后重启 inetd 进程以禁用 dtspcd 服务，或限制对 dtspcd 的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/636","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1880","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19498","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0689","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0689.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e5dfe0fd5272fb57836fe5d2345c8106633847cd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c3dc2ea0-0265-4c0c-ae08-6be3c238c97a.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0255","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0691","title":"CDE dtaction AddSuLog 函数缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境中的 dtaction 工具的 AddSuLog 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该函数提交超长的用户名字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据，成功利用此漏洞可获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Digital UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14 及 Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0691"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.420","remediation":"各受影响厂商均已发布安全补丁：Sun 用户安装 Security Bulletin #192 提供的补丁，HP 用户应用 HPSBUX9909-103 中的 CDE 补丁，IBM AIX 4.3.2 用户安装 APAR IY07386，SGI IRIX 6.5.14 用户安装 SGID 19990901-01-P 补丁，Digital UNIX 4.0 用户安装 Compaq SSRT0584 补丁。由于所有受影响系统均已停止支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/635","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A3078","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19497","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0691","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/f24db61575bca326440113bfa8e6a6aa18028087/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/72e1ca263be82e97277404223a060b794df013c9/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/7508fe94d6cb928e2d6fa91ffa0cfae566c76517/1999/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0392","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0392.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0750","title":"Microsoft Hotmail 跨站脚本攻击漏洞","description":"Microsoft Hotmail 存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 HTML 的 STYLE 标签中嵌入恶意 JavaScript 代码，当用户使用 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 或 Netscape Communicator 4.0/4.5/4.6 等浏览器访问 Hotmail 时，恶意脚本将在用户浏览器中自动执行，导致攻击者能够以用户身份执行任意操作，包括读取、篡改或删除邮件内容。该漏洞影响 Hotmail 邮件服务，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0750"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.727","remediation":"升级到现代浏览器（IE 5.5 及以上版本已修复此问题），或改用 Chrome/Firefox/Edge 等现代浏览器，其默认安全策略禁止在 STYLE 标签中执行 JavaScript。Hotmail 用户应确保使用最新版浏览器访问邮件服务，并启用浏览器 XSS 过滤器（现代浏览器默认开启）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/630","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19492"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0392.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0392.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0392.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0759","title":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 POP 邮件服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 的 POP 邮件服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 POP 服务发送超长的 USER 或 PASS 命令触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 版本。目前厂商已停止维护，建议用户迁移至其他受支持的邮件服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0759"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.867","remediation":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 已停止维护，建议立即迁移至受支持的邮件服务器（如 Exchange、Postfix、Dovecot）。在迁移完成前，在防火墙上限制 POP 端口（110/TCP）仅允许受信任源 IP 访问，并禁用 POP 服务改用 IMAP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.crosswinds.net/~fuseware/faq.html#8","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/634","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19496","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0759.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0759","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/a1bd988e57a056ba1f06c9d4970f9f19b2540605/1999/CVE-1999-0759/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0759.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0759.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mwxf-c8hf-3mf7/GHSA-mwxf-c8hf-3mf7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0759.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0864","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1014","title":"Sun Solaris mail 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 操作系统的 /usr/bin/mail 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户向 mail 命令的 -m 参数传递超长字符串时，程序未对输入长度进行正确边界检查，导致栈缓冲区溢出。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞精心构造恶意载荷覆盖栈中返回地址，从而以 mail 命令的权限（通常为 root 或 mail 组权限）执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.7 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统账号方能利用，无需网络远程访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1014"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.477","remediation":"安装 Sun 当时发布的补丁 106827-01（SPARC）/ 106828-01（x86），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。对于仍运行 Solaris 7 的遗留系统，可移除 /usr/bin/mail 的 setuid root 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/mail）作为临时缓解，但会影响普通用户使用 mail 命令。现代系统建议迁移至受支持的 Solaris 11 或替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93727925026476&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93846422810162&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3297","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19529","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1014","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1014.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0864.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1686","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1053","title":"Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 服务端包含命令执行漏洞","description":"Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 2.3.1 存在服务器端包含（SSI）命令注入漏洞。该脚本试图通过移除 \"<!--\" 与 \"-->\" 分隔符之间的内容来过滤用户插入的 SSI 命令，但由于 Apache 1.3.9 及部分其他版本允许除 \"-->\" 以外的其他闭合序列，导致过滤机制可被绕过。远程攻击者可通过在留言内容中插入特制的 SSI 指令，在服务器上执行任意命令，进而获取系统控制权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1053"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.507","remediation":"立即停用 Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 2.3.1 及更早版本，替换为受支持的留言板程序（如用现代 PHP/Python 实现的替代品）。在 Apache 配置中对 guestbook.pl 所在目录禁用 Server-Side Include：`Options -Includes`，或通过 `RemoveHandler .shtml` 关闭 SSI 解析。如暂时无法更换，可添加 Apache rewrite 规则阻止包含 `<!--#` 的请求。同时建议在系统层面对 CGI 目录启用 `open_basedir` 等沙箱限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/33674","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27296","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27560","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/776","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9907","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1053.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/1fb9a053a31c41206e693c4b4856611d722d4df7/1999/CVE-1999-1053.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/3fc9c3bcaeabe40a6c524b4856d657e849f9160b/1999/CVE-1999-1053/CVE-1999-1053-PoC.py","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1053","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/1b8090ba645ab1c5dda2d9b5e7162904117c546d/1999/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-1053.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1053.json","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://g